title: New Launch Partner: Composable Finance
body:
## Sentence Summary
We're looking to sign on Composable Finance ([website](https://www.composable.finance/)) as a launch partner.

## Detailed Summary
The Launch Partner program at Polywrap benefits both our partners and the Polywrap project. 

For our partners, it means that they'll receive priority help when building their polywrapper and receive first access to beta versions for new products, such as the hub.   We'll have regular calls with our partners.  We'll also invite them to join our Discord where they can ask questions in #help.

For our project, we choose partners who believe that Polywrap is a solution to their problems.  It's a no-commitment program, but in the past, some benefits to our project include getting feedback on our code and docs.

## Motivation
Composable Finance is building an Ethereum cross-L2 communication SDK for a multi-L2 future.  We believe their use-case is very unique and that a Composable Finance polywrapper can be more beneficial for their project rather than a JS SDK.

Jordan and I spoke to their team on Oct 8 2021.  They have a great understanding of our project and how it can benefit them.

## Proposal Options
#1: Accept
#2: Reject
